  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to verify that the frequency of pancreatic fistula (ISGPF grade B
      and C) in horizontal mattress suture are lower than in interrupted suture during
      pancreaticojejunostomy in pancreatoduodenectomy by randomized clinical trial.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
